The Cervix is the lowermost part of the Uterus (womb) which projects into the upper part of the Vagina. #CervicalCancer
The incidence/development of #CervicalCancer has been closely linked with infection by several strains of HPV (Human Papilloma Virus).
HPV is a sexually transmitted pathogen hence #CervicalCancer in some quarters is referred to as Sexually Transmitted Cancer.
Early stages of #CervicalCancer can be asymptomatic and hence can undiagnosed for several years & thus many cases in Sub-Saharan Africa 1/2
Are known in late/advanced stages. It is pertinent that Females especially sexually active ones check themselves often. #CervicalCancer
The advent of an effective vaccine for several strains (subtypes) of HPV has led to significant reduction in the incidence of#CervicalCancer
This reduction is evident in western countries where routine immunization of school age females has been implemented. #CervicalCancer
